- `ports` ‚Üí map port 5678 ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á container ‚Üí port 5678 ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á host (‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ Nginx ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ)

  - `WEBHOOK_TUNNEL_URL` ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ `WEBHOOK_URL` ‚Üí ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå webhook ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á
  - `GENERIC_TIMEZONE` ‚Üí ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á timezone ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ (UTC ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ Asia/Bangkok)

- `networks` ‚Üí ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ bridge network ‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏û‡∏≤‡∏∞ stack ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏†‡∏±‡∏¢

## **6.1 ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á Nginx**

**‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á:**

**‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ:**

- ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏û‡πá‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏à Nginx ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å repository ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Debian/Ubuntu
- `-y` ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ auto-confirm ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏î `y` ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏´‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á

**‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ï‡∏∏‡∏ú‡∏•:**

- Nginx ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô "‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ï‡∏π‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤" ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏ó‡∏≥:
  - **SSL termination** (‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏±‡∏™ HTTPS ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà Nginx ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏™‡πà‡∏á plain HTTP ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ô)
  - **Security filtering** (‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° HTTP security headers)
  - **Reverse Proxy** ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö n8n container
  - **‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πá‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏¥‡∏£‡πå‡∏ü‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß** (‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô Virtual Host)

## **6.2 ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå config ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Nginx ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö n8n**

**‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á:**  
bash  
`sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/n8n.conf`

**‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏´‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå (‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö `n8n.example.com` ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô `n8n.thho.me`):**

`server {`  
 `listen 80;`  
 `server_name n8n.thho.me;`

    `# Redirect all HTTP traffic to HTTPS (will be added by Certbot)`
    `location / {`
        `proxy_pass http://localhost:5678;`
        `proxy_http_version 1.1;`

        `# Disable buffering for real-time functionality`
        `chunked_transfer_encoding off;`
        `proxy_buffering off;`
        `proxy_cache off;`

        `# WebSocket support for n8n's real-time features`
        `proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;`
        `proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";`

        `# Essential proxy headers for proper functionality`
        `proxy_set_header Host $host;`
        `proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;`
        `proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;`
        `proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;`

        `# Extended timeout for long-running workflows`
        `proxy_read_timeout 86400;`
        `proxy_connect_timeout 60;`
        `proxy_send_timeout 60;`
    `}`

`}`

**‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå:**

- **`listen 80`** ‚Üí ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ HTTP ‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥ (Certbot ‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° HTTPS ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á)
- **`proxy_pass http://localhost:5678;`** ‚Üí forward request ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á n8n container ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏û‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ï 5678
- **`chunked_transfer_encoding off;`** ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ **`proxy_buffering off;`** ‚Üí ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ buffer ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏• real-time ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏ñ‡∏∂‡∏á browser ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ
- **WebSocket Support** ‚Üí ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ `Upgrade` ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ `Connection "upgrade"` ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ü‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå real-time ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á n8n ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ
- **Proxy Headers** ‚Üí ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏â‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ö ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô IP ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á (`X-Real-IP`)
- **Timeout** ‚Üí 86400 ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ (24 ‡∏ä‡∏±‡πà‡∏ß‡πÇ‡∏°‡∏á) ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö workflow ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ô

**‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏î:**

2. `nginx -t` ‚Üí ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö syntax ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á config ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô error ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô restart

   - ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ Nginx proxy ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î firewall ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á port 5678 ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å public internet ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô Nginx ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô

   - ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ Certbot ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô HTTPS ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° auto-renew

## **7.1 ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á Certbot**

**‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á:**

bash  
`#!/bin/bash`

`# 1. ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏õ`

`services:`  
 `n8n:`

 `restart: always`

 `ports:`  
 `- "5678:5678"`

 `- n8n_data:/home/node/.n8n`  
 `- ~/.n8n/config:/home/node/.n8n/config`  
 `networks:`  
 `- n8n_network`

`runner:`  
 `image: n8nio/n8n:latest`  
 `restart: always`  
 `environment:`  
 `- N8N_RUNNERS_ENABLED=true`  
 `- N8N_RUNNERS_HOST=n8n`  
 `- N8N_RUNNERS_PROTOCOL=https`  
 `- N8N_RUNNERS_AUTH_BASIC=true`  
 `volumes:`  
 `- ~/.n8n/config:/home/node/.n8n/config`

 `- n8n`

 `- n8n_network`

`networks:`  
 `n8n_network:`

`volumes:`  
 `n8n_data:`

`cat > ~/.n8n/config << 'EOF'`

    `listen 443 ssl http2;`
    `ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/n8n.thho.me/fullchain.pem;`
    `ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/n8n.thho.me/privkey.pem;`

    `location / {`
        `proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:5678;`

        `proxy_cache off;`

        `proxy_read_timeout 86400;`
        `proxy_connect_timeout 60;`
        `proxy_send_timeout 60;`
    `}`

`}`

`server {`  
 `listen 80;`  
 `server_name n8n.thho.me;`  
 `return 301 https://$host$request_uri;`  
`}`  
`EOF`

 `DC_CMD="docker compose"`

 `echo "$LOG_TAG $1"`  
`}`

`backup_data() {`  
 `mkdir -p "$BACKUP_DIR"`  
 `BACKUP_FILE="$BACKUP_DIR/n8n-backup-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).tar.gz"`  
 `log "üì¶ ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á Backup..."`  
 `docker run --rm -v "$VOLUME_NAME":/data -v "$BACKUP_DIR":/backup alpine \`  
 `tar czf "/backup/$(basename "$BACKUP_FILE")" -C /data .`  
 `log "‚úÖ Backup ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à: $BACKUP_FILE"`

    `find "$BACKUP_DIR" -type f -name "*.tar.gz" -mtime +7 -exec rm {} \; || true`

`}`

`restore_backup() {`  
 `echo "üìÇ ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå Backup ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Å‡∏π‡πâ:"`  
 `select FILE in "$BACKUP_DIR"/*.tar.gz; do`  
 `if [ -n "$FILE" ]; then`  
 `log "‚ôªÔ∏è ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏π‡πâ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å $FILE"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down`  
 `docker run --rm -v "$VOLUME_NAME":/data -v "$FILE":/backup.tar.gz alpine \`  
 `sh -c "rm -rf /data/* && tar xzf /backup.tar.gz -C /data"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `break`  
 `fi`  
 `done`  
`}`

`restore_latest() {`  
 `FILE=$(ls -t "$BACKUP_DIR"/*.tar.gz 2>/dev/null | head -n 1 || true)`  
 `if [ -n "$FILE" ]; then`  
 `log "‚ôªÔ∏è ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏π‡πâ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å $FILE"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down`  
 `docker run --rm -v "$VOLUME_NAME":/data -v "$FILE":/backup.tar.gz alpine \`  
 `sh -c "rm -rf /data/* && tar xzf /backup.tar.gz -C /data"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `else`  
 `log "‚ùå ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå Backup"`  
 `fi`  
`}`

`generate_compose() {`  
`cat << YAML > "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE"`  
`version: '3.9'`  
`services:`  
 `n8n:`  
 `container_name: n8n`  
 `image: $IMAGE_NAME`  
 `restart: always`  
 `ports:`  
 `- "5678:5678"`  
 `environment:`  
 `- N8N_TRUST_PROXY=true`  
 `- N8N_BASIC_AUTH_ACTIVE=false`  
 `- N8N_ENFORCE_SETTINGS_FILE_PERMISSIONS=true`  
 `- N8N_RUNNERS_ENABLED=true`  
 `volumes:`  
 `- n8n_data:/home/node/.n8n`

`volumes:`  
 `n8n_data:`  
`YAML`  
`}`

`maintenance_tasks() {`  
 `log "üîÑ Restart nginx..."`  
 `sudo systemctl restart nginx`  
 `log "üîë Renew SSL..."`  
 `sudo certbot renew --quiet`  
 `log "üìú ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö Log n8n..."`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" logs --tail=30 n8n || true`  
`}`

`# ===== MENU =====`  
`if [[ "${1:-}" == "--auto" ]]; then`  
 `log "‚öôÔ∏è ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î Full Maintenance ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥"`  
 `backup_data`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down`  
 `docker pull "$IMAGE_NAME"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `exit 0`  
`fi`

`echo "========= Manage n8n ========="`  
`echo "1. Full Reset + Backup"`  
`echo "2. Restart + Backup"`  
`echo "3. Restore ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå"`  
`echo "4. Restore ‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î"`  
`echo "5. Update + Backup"`  
`echo "6. Full Maintenance (Backup + Update + Renew SSL + Restart nginx + Log)"`  
`read -p "‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏Ç: " choice`

`case $choice in`  
 `1)`  
 `backup_data`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down -v`  
 `docker pull "$IMAGE_NAME"`  
 `generate_compose`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `;;`  
 `2)`  
 `backup_data`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" restart`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `;;`  
 `3)`  
 `restore_backup`  
 `;;`  
 `4)`  
 `restore_latest`  
 `;;`  
 `5)`  
 `backup_data`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down`  
 `docker pull "$IMAGE_NAME"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `;;`  
 `6)`  
 `backup_data`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" down`  
 `docker pull "$IMAGE_NAME"`  
 `$DC_CMD -f "$DOCKER_COMPOSE_FILE" up -d`  
 `maintenance_tasks`  
 `;;`  
 `*)`  
 `log "‚ùå ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á"`  
 `;;`  
`esac`

`# ‡∏´‡∏¢‡∏∏‡∏î container ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î`

`# ‡∏•‡∏ö container ‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏´‡∏¢‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß`

   ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Å‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ ‡∏à‡∏∞ fallback ‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ `docker-compose`
